      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs-dne on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Trevis Autotest from trevis-13vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/71ac3ba5-ac80-4397-ab35-bcfbd6cac3b2 ran 4 tests.",
